1. Install georuby, xmlparser (gem install GeoRuby, aptitude install libxml-parser-ruby1.8).
2. Get OSM file with JOSM or via OSM API.
3. Do ./osm2po.rb <osm file> <lang code> > <file.po>
4. Translate
5. Do ./po2osm.rb <source osm file> <po file> <lang code> > <result.osm>
6. Upload result with JOSM.
